# Backend Rules (Laravel 12)

## PHP Conventions

```php
<?php
declare(strict_types=1);

// Constructor property promotion
public function __construct(
    private readonly CartService $cartService,
) {}

// Explicit return types always
public function show(Product $product): JsonResponse
{
    return response()->json(new ProductResource($product));
}

// casts() method — not $casts property (Laravel 12)
protected function casts(): array
{
    return ['price' => 'integer', 'status' => OrderStatus::class];
}
```

## Eloquent

- `Model::query()` always — never `DB::` for standard queries
- Eager-load relations (no N+1): `->with(['variants', 'category'])`
- `->sole()` for must-exist single result, `->firstOrFail()` when appropriate
- Translatable columns: `where('title->en', 'value')` or `whereJsonContainsLocale()`

## Controllers

- Thin controllers — business logic in `app/Services/`
- Always use Form Request classes (never inline validation)
- Always return API Resources, not raw models

## Routes

- API routes: `api.v1.` prefix under `/api/v1/`
- Admin routes: `admin.` prefix under `/admin/`
- New API endpoints need a rate limiter: `api.strict` (10/min) | `api.public` (60/min) | `api.auth` (300/min)

## Testing (Pest)

```php
declare(strict_types=1);

beforeEach(function () {
    Role::firstOrCreate(['name' => 'admin']);
});

it('creates a product', function () {
    $user = User::factory()->create()->assignRole('admin');
    $this->actingAs($user, 'sanctum')
        ->postJson('/api/v1/products', [...])
        ->assertCreated();
});
```

- `assertSoftDeleted()` — not `assertDatabaseMissing()` for soft-delete models
- `assertOk()` / `assertCreated()` / `assertUnprocessable()` — not `assertStatus(200)`
- Always use factories; create them if missing

## Enums

```php
enum OrderStatus: string
{
    case AwaitingPayment = 'awaiting_payment';  // TitleCase keys
    case Processing = 'processing';
}
```

## After Changes

Run: `docker compose exec php vendor/bin/pint --dirty`
Run: `docker compose exec php php artisan test --compact`

## Admin SPA (Inertia + React)

- Pages in `resources/js/pages/admin/`
- Use Wayfinder: `import { index } from '@/actions/Admin/ProductController'`
- Forms: `<Form>` Inertia component
- Navigation: `<Link>` Inertia component
- Run after admin route changes: `docker compose exec php php artisan wayfinder:generate --no-interaction`
